reviewText: The DVDs would not play in any of my DVD players without skipping or stopping altogether. Wasn't able to return this item, but Amazon was kind enough to give me a refund. I just threw the DVDs away :(

I am basically into old movies to 1970 and some of 1980s and traditional and classical dances of India.. However the discs have number of favourites from the Hit movies. Regardless the dances from the new movies are also spectacular in color, music and costumes.
Love this collection of songs and dances.

If you have patience to sit back,relax.enjoy the era of 1950's and 1960's look no further the ship has landed as the dances are fantastic,
most actors and actresses gone,but their beauty.glamour ,real acting talents,dancing,the set decorations are enormous ,a real treat.
you may get one or two good songs out of this
